data.description: Big price adjustment on this charmer! What a great value for a renovated 3 bedroom cottage (2 per tax) that's move in ready, just bring your toothbrush! Enjoy the charming front porch swing looking out to a grassy lawn sheltered by stunning oak trees with just the right amount of shade. Once inside you'll find a light and bright living room and a large renovated kitchen with slab Carrera marble countertops and stainless appliances. The oversized dining room adjacent to the kitchen features access to the spacious entertainer's delight of a backyard, perfect for enjoying the warm Sonoma evenings outdoors. This private backyard is fully fenced with an elevated BBQ and dining deck, a grassy zone for little ones and pets, a fire circle area and even a sunny zone for your veggie garden. Back inside, you'll find a beautifully renovated bathroom with designer tile and heated floors, 3 bedrooms off the charming paneled hallway with designer fixtures, the third bedroom leads out french doors to the backyard. This fabulous location is just a short stroll to the Boyes Hot Springs restaurant scene and just a 7 min drive to the Sonoma Square or Kenwood/Glen Ellen. Tesla EV charger, A/C and charming porch swing included!
